Usage: load_timing_debug_report [-help] {{<file> [-name <string>]}|{ -proto  [-additional_slack_past_wns <float>] [-num_path <integer>]}}

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
<file>                                 # Specifies the name of the timing debug
                                       # file. (string, required)
-additional_slack_past_wns <float>     # Plus the additional specified slack
                                       # (float, optional)
-name <string>                         # Specifies the report name to load the
                                       # machine readable timing report files
                                       # incrementally. (string, optional)
-num_path <integer>                    # Number of paths to be reported in path
                                       # violations (int, optional)
-proto                                 # Specifies the FlexModel prototyping.
                                       # (bool, required)